    section.bottom-rule.getting-started
      h2 Getting started
      p Start by creating a 
        code package.json
        | :

      .highlight.highlight-bash
        pre npm init

      p Install hapi and save it to your 
        code package.json
        |  dependencies:

      .highlight.highlight-bash
        pre npm install hapi --save

      p Create a
        code server.js
        |  file with the following contents:

      .highlight.highlight-javascript
        pre
          span.pl-s1
            span.pl-pds '
            | use strict
            span.pl-pds '
          | ;
          br

          br
